&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Some drops are hard as stone &lt;br>
It takes millions of years to make &lt;br>
them and millions to dissolve.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Some drops are like salt ball &lt;br>
It takes longer to make them &lt;br>
but they dissolve quickly.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Some drops have a dirty smell &lt;br>
When those merge into the ocean &lt;br>
for some time there is a bad smell around them &lt;br>
but very soon they also disappear.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>